0005#STR0005#ALL#Caption -
0006#STR0006#ALL#01 - Available Time  , according to the scale
0007#STR0007#ALL#02 - Absent Time  
0008#STR0008#ALL#03 - Real Time     = Available Time   - Absent Time  
0009#STR0009#ALL#04 - Time without application or stopped. 
0010#STR0010#ALL#05 - Worked or Applied Time      
0011#STR0011#ALL#06 - Extra time , or Time applied OUT of the normal scale
0012#STR0012#ALL#07 - Bursted time or total of time executed outside the table.    
0013#STR0013#ALL#08 - Standard time
0014#STR0014#ALL#09 - Charged Time or Standard Time with increases or decreases.  
0015#STR0015#ALL#10 - Time actually Sold             
0016#STR0016#ALL#11 - User choice criterion, whose result to be obtained through the use of formula created by it
0017#STR0017#ALL#12 - % Efficiency on Standard Time (Standard Time/Applied Time) * 100
0018#STR0018#ALL#13 - % Efficiency on Standard Time (Standard Time/(Applied Time + Overtime)) * 100
0019#STR0019#ALL#14 - % Efficiency on Collected Time (Collected Time / Applied Time) * 100
0020#STR0020#ALL#15 - % Efficiency on Collected Time (Collected Time/(Applied Time + Overtime)) * 100
0021#STR0021#ALL#16 - % Efficiency on Sold Time (Sold Time / Applied Time) * 100
0022#STR0022#ALL#17 - % Efficiency on Sold Time (Sold Time/(Applied Time + Overtime)) * 100
0023#STR0023#ALL#19 - % Productivity on Real Time          (Applied Time / Real Time    )
0024#STR0024#ALL#20 - % Productivity on Real Time            (Applied Time  + Extra Time )/Real Time    )
0025#STR0025#ALL#21 - % Performance (collected time/default time) * 100
0026#STR0026#ALL#22 - % Performance (worked time/available time) * 100
0027#STR0027#ALL#23 - Hours Applied and Not approved
